{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "孟元超与师妹吕思美遭点苍双煞段仇世、卜天雕围攻，形势危急。云紫萝蒙面从假山石后飞出，以三招精妙剑法击退双煞——削掉段仇世半边头发，刺穿卜天雕劳宫穴废其毒掌。云紫萝救完人即刻离去，不愿让孟元超认出自己。孟元超虽未看清面容，却从背影感到似曾相识。夜间孟元超吹箫怀念旧情，云紫萝在林中听到箫声却无法回头。杨牧戴人皮面具暗中跟踪，先向点苍双煞献计利用孟元超的私生子逼其磕头，又取出孟元超留给云紫萝的家传汉玉作为信物。但段仇世拒绝了杨牧的卑鄙提议，掌击杨牧将其赶走。杨牧怀恨在心，转而被御林军副统领石朝玑胁迫，答应充当清廷暗探。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "臭丫头，你有眼无珠，胆敢伤我，我也不要你性命，只要你的两只眼珠！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "孟元超，你还要硬充好汉么？可惜，可惜！可惜你这身武功。我本来不想取你性命的，你却非要送死不可！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穷寇莫追，请恩公回来，受我一拜！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "我歇一歇就没事了。咱们多亏那人相救，你去请她回来吧。但她是个女子，你看不出来吗？可别恩公恩公的乱嚷了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "小师妹，你不要逞强了，我扶你回房歇息吧。我知道你想报恩，但那位恩人倘若愿意和咱们见面，她自己会回来的，倘若她不肯和我们见面，我去追也追不上。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "奇怪，她为什么救了咱们，又避免和咱们见面，你可猜想得到她是谁吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "我怎么知道？你的身体要紧，别管她是谁了，早点儿歇息吧。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "师哥，可是她回来了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "你说谁呀？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "瞧你这副失魂落魄的样子，你以为我说的是谁？当然是那个神龙见首不见尾的女子了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "你还在想着她？她早已去得远了，不会再回来了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "咦，你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "你不是说她是神龙见首不见尾么？我的看法也是如此。她若要见咱们，那就不会走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "哦，那么你不是在想她却又想谁？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "你以前看护我的病，时常给我唱歌。我不会唱歌，吹萧给你听好不好？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "好呀，好呀！我记得在小金川的时候，你和宋帅哥常常一个吹萧一个唱曲的。我已经有许久没听过你吹萧了。",
      "tone": "喜悦",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "可惜腾霄不在这儿，没人给你唱曲。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "我倒是有点佩服孟元超呢！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "什么？昨晚你也是吃了他们的亏的，怎的却佩服起仇人来了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "其实孟元超并不是咱们的仇人，咱们的仇人是他的师父。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "我的毒功断送，就是因他而起，你也给他的师妹斩了一刀，你还说他不是咱们的仇人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "你也说得不错，经过了昨晚这一战，咱们当然也是和孟元超结下了粱子的了。但我还是禁不住佩服他。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "你佩服孟元超什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "我佩服他是一条硬汉子，还有他那一路刀法，我也很是佩服。说老实话，单打独斗，我们都不是他的对手，昨晚得见吕寿昆衣钵真传的刀法，也算得是不虚此行了。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "如此说来，这个仇你是不想报了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "这也不然，佩服和报仇是两件事。不过我倒想用另一个法子报仇。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "我还未曾想得出来，不过我是不想和他性命相斗了。我要把本领练得比他高明，叫他甘拜下风。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "我是不行的了，但愿你好歹也给咱们出这口气。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu",
      "text": "你这个三分像人七分像鬼的东西，鬼鬼祟祟地跟在我们后面干吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "卜先生，请你不要骂人，我看你现在也是狼狈得很，样子并不见得怎样好看啊！",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "好呀，你这个鬼东西居然敢讥笑我，你老子今晚虽然打输了架，要打发你谅还可以！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "何必如此动怒，你焉知道我是对你没有好处的呢？",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "真人不露相，露相不真人。阁下大约是不想给我们知道你是谁吧？好，那我也就不请问阁下的高姓大名了，只是想请问阁下有何指教？",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "段先生不愧是爽快的人，那我也就爽诀的说了。实不相瞒，你们昨晚之事，我都已知道，你们要不要向孟元超报仇？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "要又怎样？你的武功虽然不错，未必打得过孟元超。哼，哼，要是我没受伤，我看你至多不过和我打个平手罢了，你又焉能帮助我们报仇？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "不错，我是打不过孟元超。但不能力敌，便当智取。只要你们依计行事，我自有办法叫孟元超跪在你们面前，给你们磕头！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "你当真有这能耐？好，你办得到孟元超给我们磕头，我给你磕头。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "那倒不必。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "师弟，我知道你不想杀掉孟元超，若能令得他给咱们磕头，这个仇我也可以当作是已经报了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "但我倒是很想知道，阁下为何这样热心，要为我们报仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "实不相瞒，我和孟元超也是结有梁子，并不仅仅是为了你们。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "哦，原来如此！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "所以你们如果是同意的话，咱们倒不妨彼此合作，做一宗交易。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "你算是找到了买主了。这是一宗见不得光的交易吧？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "不错，现在天还未亮，这的确是见不得光的买卖。",
      "tone": "喜悦",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "有话快说，有屁快放，你的办法如何？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "孟元超有个好朋友，名叫宋腾霄，这个人你们想必知道？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "他们在小金川的时候，是焦不离孟，孟不离焦的。听说这人的武功不在孟元超之下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "我见过他的武功，比孟元超稍差一点，孟元超有个孩子。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "胡说八道，孟元超还未娶妻，哪里来的孩子？你这不是存心来骗我们吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "卜兄，你这是只知其一，不知其二。未成亲也可以有孩子的，这是孟元超的私生子！",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "公的和母的住在起就会有孩子，不一定要拜堂成亲？对，对，你是说得不错，但这又怎样？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "这个孩子，如今正由宋腾霄将他带来苏州。他们走的是大路，你们很容易就可以在路上找着他。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "哦，原来你是要在这孩子的身上做文章。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "不错，咱们报仇的办法就是要着落在这孩子的身上。宋腾霄的武功虽也不弱，但他要保护孩子，决计不是你们的对手。你们可以在他的手上把这孩子夺来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "我们要一个小孩子干吗？没的自讨麻烦！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "孟元超的孩子在你们手上，你们要他如何就是如何，他还敢不依。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "是呀，这样简单的道理，我怎样没有想起！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "孟元超从未见过这个孩子，你们说的他未必相信。但他不认识这个孩子，这块玉他是一定认识的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "你们把孟元超的儿子抢了过来，将这块玉挂在他的颈上，就可以带他去见孟元超了。不错，孟元超是个硬汉子，但三个响头交换自己的亲生骨肉，我想，这三个响头，只怕孟元超还是非磕不可的了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "好，好！这个办法好极了！",
      "tone": "喜悦",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "不错，这样一来，我们的仇算是报了。但在这宗交易之中，你想得到的好处又是什么？",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "我要得孟元超的性命。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "哦，你和孟元超竟有这样的不共戴天之仇吗？不过，他既然给我磕头，我可不能替你杀他了。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "用不着你们动手，在他向你们磕头的时候，我自会用暗器取他性命。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段仇世",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "还有什么另外的条件吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "有。不过，这可要稍微委屈你们了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "你帮了我们这个大忙，我们稍稍受点委屈也算不了什么，你说吧。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "事情过后，我会偷偷跟在你们后面，第二天方始在路上会见你们。那时我的装束可能完全改变，变成了和现在大不相同的另一个人。不过我的声音你们当然是记得的，是吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "当然记得。但你这样做却是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "我要那个孩子。请你们千万不要说穿你们是认识我的。我见了你们之后，会装出大怒的神气，痛骂你们，并且和你们动手，请你们不要见怪。你们装作给我打败，让我把孩子抢去。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "要我们点苍双煞败在你手下，这不能！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "text": "那就让我吃点亏了，你可以打我一掌，甚至把我打伤，但最后你们还是要让我把孩子抢去才行。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_diao",
      "speaker_name": "卜天雕",
      "listener": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "text": "好，这样倒还可以。反正我不想要那野孩子。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu_disguised",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_duan_qiu_shi",
      "text": "段大哥，这块玉交给你了。三天之后，晚上三更时分，我在那个园子，恭候你们两位的大驾。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7
    }
